iade 2015','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/29/english-olympiade-2015','Prodi Pendidikan Bahaasa Inggris','2016-11-05','20:50:09'),(324,'Seminar Kesehatan \"Gizi Sehat Seimbang Menuju Hidup Berkualitas\"','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/30/seminar-kesehatan-gizi-sehat-seimbang-menuju-hidup-berkualitas-','','2016-11-05','20:50:09'),(325,'Olimpiade Matematika 2015','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/31/olimpiade-matematika-2015','','2016-11-05','20:50:10'),(326,'Haflah Miladiyah VIII Pendidikan Guru Madrasah Ibtidaiyah','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/32/haflah-miladiyah-viii-pendidikan-guru-madrasah-ibtidaiyah','','2016-11-05','20:50:12'),(327,'FESTIVAL ARABY 2015 SE-JAWA TIMUR','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/33/festival-araby-2015-se-jawa-timur','','2016-11-05','20:50:13'),(328,'Haflah Miladiyah PAI 2015','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/34/haflah-miladiyah-pai-2015','','2016-11-05','20:50:14'),(329,'Seminar Kesehatan \"Tema : Sakit Tifus, Kenali Tanda Gejalanya\"','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/35/seminar-kesehatan-tema-sakit-tifus-kenali-tanda-gejalanya-','','2016-11-05','20:50:14'),(330,'Multicultural Day \"Celebrating Diversity; Knowing Cultures, Knowing Each Other\"','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/36/multicultural-day-celebrating-diversity-knowing-cultures-knowing-each-other-','International Office','2016-11-05','20:50:15'),(331,'LPM Solidaritas UIN Sunan Ampel Surabaya \"LOMBA ESAI NASIONAL\"','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/37/lpm-solidaritas-uin-sunan-ampel-surabaya-lomba-esai-nasional-','','2016-11-05','20:50:16'),(332,'International Day For The Elimination Of Violence Againts Women','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/38/international-day-for-the-elimination-of-violence-againts-women','','2016-11-05','20:50:17'),(333,'Wisuda Hafid 1 UPTQ','http://www.uinsby.ac.id/agenda/id/39/wisuda-hafid-1-uptq','','2016-11-05','20:50:18');

